*Oni* su veoma srećni. (They are very happy.)
Svi *oni* su došli. (All of them came.)
Oni su se smejali. (*They* were laughing.)
Nisam svega toga lično videla, ali *oni* kažu da je to istina. (I haven't seen all of that myself, but *they* say it's true.)
*Oni* su krivi za to. (They are to blame for it.)